---
const title = 'OpenClaw 中文网 — 真正能做事的开源 AI 助手';
const description =
  'OpenClaw 是开源自托管的个人 AI 智能体，支持 WhatsApp、Telegram、Discord、飞书、钉钉、企业微信等 20+ 聊天平台。运行在你自己的电脑上，数据完全私有，一键安装。';
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/assets/og-default.png" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="OpenClaw 中文网" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="zh_CN" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/pixel-lobster.svg" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fragment+Mono&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      :root {
        --oc-coral: #ff5a36;
        --oc-coral-dark: #e84e2c;
        --oc-text: #1a1a2e;
        --oc-text-secondary: #64748b;
        --oc-text-muted: #94a3b8;
        --oc-bg: #fff;
        --oc-bg-card: #fff;
        --oc-border: #e5e7eb;
        --oc-bg-elevated: #f8f9fa;
        color-scheme: light dark;
      }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --oc-text: #f0f4ff;
          --oc-text-secondary: #8892b0;
          --oc-text-muted: #5a6480;
          --oc-bg: #0a0f1a;
          --oc-bg-card: rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.8);
          --oc-border: rgba(136, 146, 176, 0.15);
          --oc-bg-elevated: #0a0f1a;
        }
      }
      body {
        font-family: 'Fragment Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
        background: var(--oc-bg);
        color: var(--oc-text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }
      .oc-container {
        max-width: 860px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
      }
      .oc-center {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .oc-accent {
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .oc-section {
        margin-bottom: 56px;
      }
      .oc-section-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .oc-section-title {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        color: var(--oc-text);
      }
      .oc-section-link {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .oc-section-link:hover {
        color: #00e5cc;
      }

      /* ── Topbar ── */
      .oc-topbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .oc-topbar-logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .oc-topbar-logo img {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
      }
      .oc-topbar-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .oc-topbar-links a {
        color: var(--oc-text-secondary);
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .oc-topbar-links a:hover {
        color: var(--oc-coral);
      }

      /* ── Hero ── */
      .oc-hero {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 56px;
        padding-top: 60px;
      }
      .oc-lobster-icon {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        animation: oc-float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .oc-lobster-icon img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }
      @keyframes oc-float {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
      }
      .oc-title {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 4.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .oc-tagline {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .oc-description {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-secondary);
        max-width: 780px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      /* ── Latest Post ── */
      .oc-latest-post-card {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .oc-latest-post-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.25);
      }
      .oc-latest-post-badge {
        padding: 3px 8px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: var(--oc-coral);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      .oc-latest-post-title {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      /* ── Testimonials ── */
      .oc-testimonials {
        margin-bottom: 56px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .oc-testimonials .oc-section-header {
        padding: 0 24px;
        max-width: 860px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
      }
      .oc-testimonials-track {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          transparent,
          black 5%,
          black 95%,
          transparent
        );
        -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          transparent,
          black 5%,
          black 95%,
          transparent
        );
      }
      .oc-testimonials-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        width: max-content;
        padding: 8px 0;
      }
      .oc-row-1 {
        animation: oc-scroll-left 80s linear infinite;
      }
      .oc-row-2 {
        animation: oc-scroll-right 90s linear infinite;
      }
      .oc-testimonials-track:hover .oc-testimonials-row {
        animation-play-state: paused;
      }
      @keyframes oc-scroll-left {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
      }
      @keyframes oc-scroll-right {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }
      .oc-testimonial-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
        min-width: 320px;
        max-width: 400px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        color: var(--oc-text);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .oc-testimonial-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-testimonial-avatar {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        border: 2px solid var(--oc-border);
        object-fit: cover;
      }
      .oc-testimonial-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 6px;
        min-width: 0;
      }
      .oc-testimonial-quote {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: var(--oc-text-secondary);
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .oc-testimonial-author {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--oc-coral);
      }

      /* ── Quick Start ── */
      .oc-quickstart-wrapper {
        max-width: 750px;
        margin: -1rem auto 0;
        padding: 0 24px 2rem;
      }
      .oc-quickstart-note {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 56px;
      }
      .oc-tabs {
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
      }
      .oc-tabs-header {
        display: flex;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        overflow-x: auto;
      }
      .oc-tab-btn {
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background: none;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-family: inherit;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
        white-space: nowrap;
        border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .oc-tab-btn:hover {
        color: var(--oc-text);
      }
      .oc-tab-btn.active {
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        border-bottom-color: var(--oc-coral);
      }
      .oc-tab-panel {
        display: none;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .oc-tab-panel.active {
        display: block;
      }
      .oc-tab-panel pre {
        background: #1a1a2e;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin: 12px 0;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .oc-tab-panel code {
        font-family: 'Fragment Mono', monospace;
      }
      .oc-tab-panel a {
        color: var(--oc-coral);
      }

      /* ── Features Grid ── */
      .oc-features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .oc-features-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }
      }
      .oc-feature-card {
        display: block;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      }
      .oc-feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-feature-icon {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .oc-feature-title {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .oc-feature-desc {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      /* ── Integrations ── */
      .oc-integrations-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .oc-integration-pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-secondary);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      }
      .oc-integration-pill:hover {
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-integrations-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .oc-integrations-links a {
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .oc-integrations-links a:hover {
        color: #00e5cc;
      }
      .oc-link-separator {
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
      }

      /* ── Press ── */
      .oc-press-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 20px;
      }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .oc-press-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
      .oc-press-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 24px 28px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .oc-press-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-press-logo {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--oc-text-secondary);
      }
      .oc-press-quote {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .oc-press-author {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--oc-coral);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      /* ── CTA Grid ── */
      .oc-cta-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .oc-cta-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        }
      }
      .oc-cta {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 24px 16px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      }
      .oc-cta:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
      }
      .oc-cta-discord:hover {
        border-color: #5865f2;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.2);
      }
      .oc-cta-docs:hover {
        border-color: #00e5cc;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 229, 204, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-cta-github:hover {
        border-color: var(--oc-text);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .oc-cta-skills:hover {
        border-color: #fbbf24;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-cta-label {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .oc-cta-sub {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
      }

      /* ── Sponsors ── */
      .oc-sponsors-grid {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 40px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .oc-sponsor-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px 32px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--oc-border);
        background: var(--oc-bg-card);
        transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      }
      .oc-sponsor-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: var(--oc-coral);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(255, 90, 54, 0.15);
      }
      .oc-sponsor-logo {
        height: 36px;
        width: auto;
        opacity: 0.7;
        transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
        object-fit: contain;
        filter: invert(1);
      }
      .oc-sponsor-card:hover .oc-sponsor-logo {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        .oc-sponsor-logo {
          filter: none;
          opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .oc-sponsor-card:hover .oc-sponsor-logo {
          opacity: 1;
          filter: none;
        }
      }

      /* ── Footer ── */
      .oc-footer {
        padding: 40px 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--oc-text-muted);
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      /* ── Mobile ── */
      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .oc-hero {
          padding-top: 40px;
        }
        .oc-lobster-icon {
          width: 80px;
          height: 80px;
        }
        .oc-cta {
          padding: 20px 12px;
        }
        .oc-cta-label {
          font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .oc-testimonial-card {
          min-width: 280px;
          max-width: 320px;
          padding: 12px;
        }
        .oc-testimonial-avatar {
          width: 36px;
          height: 36px;
        }
        .oc-sponsors-grid {
          gap: 16px;
        }
        .oc-sponsor-card {
          padding: 16px 24px;
        }
        .oc-sponsor-logo {
          height: 28px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Topbar -->
    <nav class="oc-topbar">
      <a href="/" class="oc-topbar-logo">
        <img src="/assets/pixel-lobster.svg" alt="OpenClaw" />
        <span>OpenClaw 中文网</span>
      </a>
      <div class="oc-topbar-links">
        <a href="/docs-home">文档</a>
        <a href="/start/getting-started">快速开始</a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a
        >
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="oc-hero">
      <div class="oc-container oc-center">
        <div class="oc-lobster-icon">
          <img src="/assets/openclaw-hero.svg" alt="OpenClaw" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="oc-title">OpenClaw</h1>
        <p class="oc-tagline">The AI that actually does things.</p>
        <p class="oc-description">
          清理收件箱、发送邮件、管理日历、自动值机。<br />
          通过 WhatsApp、Telegram 或任何你已经在用的聊天应用。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Latest Post -->
    <div class="oc-container oc-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <a
        href="https://openclaw.ai/blog/virustotal-partnership"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="oc-latest-post-card"
      >
        <span class="oc-latest-post-badge">New</span>
        <span class="oc-latest-post-title"
          >OpenClaw 与 VirusTotal 合作保障 Skill 安全 →</span
        >
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div class="oc-testimonials">
      <div class="oc-container">
        <div class="oc-section-header">
          <h2 class="oc-section-title">
            <span class="oc-accent">⟩</span> 用户评价
          </h2>
          <a
            href="https://openclaw.ai/shoutouts"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="oc-section-link">查看全部 →</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="oc-testimonials-track">
        <div class="oc-testimonials-row oc-row-1">
          <a
            class="oc-testimonial-card"
            href="https://x.com/therno/status/2014216984267780431"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <img
              src="https://unavatar.io/x/therno"
              alt="therno"
              class="oc-testimonial-avatar"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="oc-testimonial-content">
              <p class="oc-testimonial-quote">"它在运营我的公司。"</p>
              <span class="oc-testimonial-author">@therno</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            class="oc-testimonial-card"
            href="https://x.com/karpathy/status/2005692186470514904"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <img
              src="https://unavatar.io/x/karpathy"
              alt="karpathy"
              class="oc-testimonial-avatar"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="oc-testimonial-content">
              <p class="oc-testimonial-quote">
                "阅读体验很棒，谢谢。喜欢 Oracle 和 Claw。"
              </p>
              <span class="oc-testimonial-author">@karpathy</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            class="oc-testimonial-card"
            href="https://x.com/davemorin/status/2013723700668096605"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <img
              src="https://unavatar.io/x/davemorin"
              alt="davemorin"
              class="oc-testimonial-avatar"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="oc-testimonial-content">
              <p class="oc-testimonial-quote">
                "我甚至不知道该怎么称呼 OpenClaw。这是全新的事物。用了几周后，这是自
                ChatGPT 发布以来，我第一次感觉自己活在未来。"
              </p>
              <span class="oc-testimonial-author">@davemorin</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            class="oc-testimonial-card"
            href="https://x.com/crossiBuilds/status/2008478023826153665"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
