          <pre><code># 安装 OpenClaw
npm i -g openclaw

# 认识你的龙虾
openclaw onboard</code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="oc-tab-panel" id="tab-source">
          <p>适合喜欢读源码的你。</p>
          <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git
cd openclaw && pnpm install && pnpm run build
pnpm run openclaw onboard</code></pre>
        </div>
